</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[165,1068,3289,3323]" pageId="159" pageNumber="762" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="159.[165,1371,2904,3479]" box="[165,1068,3289,3323]" pageId="159" pageNumber="762">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[165,401,3289,3323]" pageId="159" pageNumber="762">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Middle ShaggyRats are nocturnal and diurnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
